Tetreault's contribution features comparative evaluation involving the author's own centering-based pronoun resolution algorithm called the Left-Right Centering algorithm (LRC) as well as three other pronoun resolution methods: Hobbs's naive algorithm (Hobbs 1978), BFP (Brennan, Friedman, and Pollard 1987), and Strube's Slist approach (Strube 1998).
